Roma keeper Alisson Becker is willing to prioritise a move to Real Madrid, despite reported interest from Liverpool, PSG &amp; Chelsea. It remains to be seen if Real Madrid want to sign a new goalkeeper despite rumours linking them to Alisson, as they have no manager. [@marca] #LFC<br />
<br />
@hugocerezo says the departure of Zidane could benefit Alisson's desire to move to Real, as the Frenchman didn't want another goalkeeper. Hugo also said that Real Madrid are unlikely to want to pay for than &euro;60M (&pound;52.5M) for the keeper.

